♪ How could it be
that what you need the most ♪

38:47.250 --> 38:49.417
♪ Can leave you feeling
just like a ghost? ♪

38:49.417 --> 38:54.000
♪ You never want to feel
so sad and lost again ♪

38:54.000 --> 38:55.542
♪ One day you
could be looking ♪

38:55.542 --> 38:57.708
♪ Through an old book
in rainy weather ♪

38:57.708 --> 39:00.750
♪ You see a picture of her
smiling at you ♪

39:00.750 --> 39:02.250
♪ When you were
still together ♪

39:02.250 --> 39:04.458
♪ You could be
walking down the street ♪

39:04.458 --> 39:07.167
♪ And who should you
chance to meet? ♪

39:07.167 --> 39:11.708
♪ That same old smile you've
been thinking of all day ♪

