♪ I'll sell the stock
we'll spend all the money ♪

39:15.959 --> 39:20.166
♪ We're starting up
a brand new day ♪

39:20.166 --> 39:22.375
♪ Turn the clock
all the way back ♪

39:22.375 --> 39:24.417
♪ I wonder
if she'll take me back ♪

39:24.417 --> 39:29.167
♪ I'm thinking
in a brand-new way ♪

39:29.167 --> 39:31.041
♪ Turn the clock
to zero boss ♪

39:31.041 --> 39:33.166
♪ The river's wide
we'll swim across ♪

39:33.166 --> 39:38.209
♪ We're starting up
a brand new day ♪

39:38.209 --> 39:41.708
♪ It could happen to you
just like it happened to me ♪

39:41.708 --> 39:45.583
♪ There's simply no immunity
there's no guarantee ♪

39:45.583 --> 39:50.458
♪ I say love's such a force
if you find yourself in it ♪

39:50.458 --> 39:52.166
♪ And sometimes
no reflection is there ♪

39:52.166 --> 39:55.125
♪ So baby wait a minute
wait a minute ♪

39:55.125 --> 39:59.834
♪ Wait a minute wait a minute
wait a minute wait a minute ♪

39:59.834 --> 40:01.750
♪ Turn the clock
to zero honey ♪

40:01.750 --> 40:04.125
♪ I'll sell the stock
we'll spend all the money ♪

40:04.125 --> 40:08.667
♪ We're starting up
a a brand-new day ♪

40:08.667 --> 40:10.333
♪ Turn the clock
to zero buddy ♪

40:10.333 --> 40:12.792
♪ Don't wanna be
no fuddy duddy ♪

40:12.792 --> 40:16.834
♪ Started up a
a brand-new day ♪

40:16.834 --> 40:18.917
♪ I'm the rhythm
in your tune ♪

40:18.917 --> 40:21.167
♪ I'm the sun
and you're the moon ♪

40:21.167 --> 40:23.125
♪ I'm a bat
and you're the cave ♪

40:23.125 --> 40:26.125
♪ You're the beach
and I'm the wave ♪

40:26.125 --> 40:28.125
♪ I'm the plow
and you're the land ♪

