♪ You're the glove
and I'm the hand ♪

40:30.375 --> 40:32.125
♪ I'm the train
and you're the station ♪

40:32.125 --> 40:33.959
♪ I'm a flagpole
to your nation ♪

40:33.959 --> 40:37.291
♪ Stand up
all you lovers in the world ♪

40:37.291 --> 40:38.959
♪ Stand up ♪

40:38.959 --> 40:40.750
♪ Stand up and be counted ♪

40:40.750 --> 40:42.458
♪ Every boy and every girl ♪

40:42.458 --> 40:47.291
♪ Stand up all you lovers
in the world yeah ♪

40:47.291 --> 40:51.291
♪ We're starting up
a brand-new day ♪

40:51.291 --> 40:54.000
♪ You're the crop
to my rotation ♪

40:54.000 --> 40:56.167
♪ You're the sum
of my equation ♪

40:56.167 --> 40:58.167
♪ I'm the answer
to your question ♪

40:58.167 --> 41:00.125
